translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 640*480, 16 colors, HDD only

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 浮遊大陸イラーピュ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Floating Continent Illapyu

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遙か上空を飛ぶその島の実体は謎に包まれていた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The true nature of the island flying high in the sky was shrouded in mystery.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 前回、光の神の逆鱗に触れランスとシィルが飛ばされたのは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Last time, Rance and Sil were thrown away after offending the Wrath of the God of Light,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そのイラーピュだった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was that Illapyu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こうして浮遊大陸での冒険が始まる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thus, the adventure on the Floating Continent begins.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大昔の王国、残された探検隊の子孫の村
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: An ancient kingdom, the village of the descendants of the abandoned exploration team.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス救援隊
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance Rescue Team

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマンの探索部隊
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Herman's Exploration Unit

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 闘神都市と呼ばれた最終兵器の遺跡
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The ruins of the ultimate weapon called the Fighting God City.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 再可動させ支配しようとするヘルマン部隊との戦い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The battle with Herman's unit attempting to reactivate and control it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おかゆの生け贄にされそうな女の子を助ける
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescue a girl who was about to be sacrificed as rice gruel.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: モガンダ博士との戦い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle against Dr. Moganda.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 蘇った闘将との戦い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle against the resurrected great warrior.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: オクトマンの巣
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Nest of Octoman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぷりょに囚われた女の子達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Girls captured by Puryo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アトランタの鏡
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Atlanta's Mirror.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 闘神υ強い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fighting God υ is strong.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルを再び掠われる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sil is kidnapped once again.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 闘神都市は落ちた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Fighting God City has fallen.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Haniho—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントを
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here are setting points that will relate later on.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's summarize them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 聖魔教団の遺産イラーピュを落とした
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Holy Demon Cult's legacy, Illapyu, was taken down.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 闘神υを倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated the Fighting God υ.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あてな２号、誕生！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Athena No.2 is born!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サーナキア、解凍！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sarnakia, defrosted!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 志津香、復讐の準備をまた邪魔される
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shizuka's preparations for revenge are interrupted again.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス５Ｄ　−ひとりぼっちの女の子−
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance 5D - The Lonely Girl -

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２００２年発売
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 2002.
640*480, Windows only.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス、シィル、あてな２号で冒険していたら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While adventuring with Rance, Sil, and Athena No.2,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 不明な場所に来てしまい迷子になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They ended up in an unknown place and got lost.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そして、深い霧を抜けた先に城を発見する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Then, beyond a deep fog, they discovered a castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 玄武城、妖怪が住んでいる不思議な城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Genbu Castle, a mysterious castle inhabited by youkai.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 城下町を放火して城内に侵入・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Set fire to the castle town and infiltrated the castle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこでひとりの少女、リズナを発見した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There, they found a girl named Rizna.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヒマワリ球根を退治したり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They defeated sunflower bulbs...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 復讐ちゃんに狙われたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Were targeted by the revenge girl...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 鬼ババアに襲われたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Were attacked by the demon hag...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この玄武城は、和華という少女が出られないよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This Genbu Castle was a prison castle where a girl named Waka couldn't leave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作られた時の止まった閉じ込め城だったが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was a castle sealed in the time it was created,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達はいくつかの謎を解き脱出に成功
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance and the others solved several mysteries and succeeded in escaping.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: めでたしめでたし
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so, happily ever after.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Haniho—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here are setting points that will be related later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィル、最期はランスに選ばれる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sil is chosen by Rance in the end.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コパンドン、ランスに惚れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Copandon falls in love with Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: バード、また不幸になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Bird becomes unfortunate again.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: Ｒａｎｃｅ６　−ゼス崩壊−
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance 6 - Collapse of Zeth -

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２００４年発売
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 2004.
640*480, Windows only.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法大国ゼスに入ったランスとシィルだが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance and Sil entered the magic superpower Zeth,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この国は、魔法使い以外は差別されてしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But in this country, anyone who is not a magic user is discriminated against.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 超差別大国であった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was a super discriminatory nation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルは優遇され貴賓扱い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sil was treated favorably and as a distinguished guest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし、ランスは奴隷と同等の扱いを受け
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, Rance was treated on par with a slave.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here are setting points that will relate later on.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's summarize them.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sarnakia, defrosted!

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shizuka's preparations for revenge are interrupted again.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance 5D - The Lonely Girl -

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２００２年発売
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 2002.
640*480, Windows only.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス、シィル、あてな２号で冒険していたら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While adventuring with Rance, Sil, and Athena No.2,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 不明な場所に来てしまい迷子になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They ended up in an unknown place and got lost.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そして、深い霧を抜けた先に城を発見する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Then, beyond a deep fog, they discovered a castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 玄武城、妖怪が住んでいる不思議な城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Genbu Castle, a mysterious castle inhabited by youkai.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 城下町を放火して城内に侵入・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Set fire to the castle town and infiltrated the castle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこでひとりの少女、リズナを発見した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There, they found a girl named Rizna.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヒマワリ球根を退治したり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They defeated sunflower bulbs...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 復讐ちゃんに狙われたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Were targeted by the revenge girl...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 鬼ババアに襲われたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Were attacked by the demon hag...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この玄武城は、和華という少女が出られないよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This Genbu Castle was a prison castle where a girl named Waka couldn't leave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作られた時の止まった閉じ込め城だったが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was a castle sealed in the time it was created,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達はいくつかの謎を解き脱出に成功
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance and the others solved several mysteries and succeeded in escaping.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: めでたしめでたし
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so, happily ever after.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Haniho—

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here are setting points that will be related later.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sil is chosen by Rance in the end.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Copandon falls in love with Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: バード、また不幸になる

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 2004.
640*480, Windows only.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法大国ゼスに入ったランスとシィルだが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance and Sil entered the magic superpower Zeth,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この国は、魔法使い以外は差別されてしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But in this country, anyone who is not a magic user is discriminated against.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 超差別大国であった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was a super discriminatory nation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルは優遇され貴賓扱い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sil was treated favorably and as a distinguished guest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし、ランスは奴隷と同等の扱いを受け
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, Rance was treated on par with a slave.
